            <p>Bates Saddles is a high end luxury saddle brand which designs and builds dressage, jump and all purpose saddles. Their customers love their horses more than life itself and are extremely critical of what they choose to strap atop their friend.</p>
            <a class="c-article__link-alone" href="https://batessaddles.com/" title="Bates Saddles Website.">batessaddles.com.au</a>
          </section>
        </div>

        <div class="u-space-md">
          <div style="--aspect-ratio:1600/940;" class="u-image-loader">
            <%= image_tag("work/bates/bates__web-banner.jpg", alt: "") %>
